snippet.textDisplay: The Pakistani Coke studio exposed our roots with utmost creative technology, and the Indian Coke studio reached into the UNIMAGINABLE DESTINATION with uniqueness, a new rhythm, and a new indulgence...BUT... Bangladesh Coke Studio mixed it all together in a single frame, in a single stage with a single master, Arnob Sayan Chowdhuri... Love to see the one music saga in these three nations... Hope, Music will heal all the remaining wounds... Love from Kolkata and Toronto
